review: Dr. Vishal is very down to earth and treats patients very nicely. I have been in contact with him for almost ten years and have never had anything bad to say about him.  He is very professional and his work is immaculate. His clinic is well equipped with modern technology machines and equipments as well.  If you are looking for a good dentist, look no further.
